  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Mealtimes feel like you're in an Italian family home - expect local ingredients and recipes full of flavour.</p>
<p>There's a classic Italian buffet breakfast served every morning to start the day.</p>
<p>In the evening you can enjoy freshly-made dishes. You'll get four courses including salad, vegetable and dessert buffets.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
