  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Schieder family have created a lovely and relaxing setting at the Hotel Dolomiti Madonna. Located in the centre of Ortisei, getting on the renowened <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomites Ski Area</a> couldn't be easier, take the escalator up to access the Seceda lift or hop on the free resort bus to access St Christina, <a data-udi="umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37d9070a8d4e4a609b9c192e453f0f97}" title="Selva">Selva</a> and Plan de Gralba. </p>
<h2>Family run</h2>
<p>The traditional Hotel Dolomiti Madonna has been in the Schieder family for almost a century, the family and their staff are attentive, helpful and on hand for anything you need to have a fantastic holiday. If you are in need of some inspiration on where to ski or a spot for lunch, be sure to ask for recommendations.</p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p>Getting on the slopes each day couldn't be easier - the nearby escalator takes you to the Seceda lift or you can use the free resort bus, which goes all around the <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Val Gardena</a> area. The hotel itself is located in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/25bd5cd4785146bd807ffe23f0747809" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25bd5cd4785146bd807ffe23f0747809}" title="Ortisei">Ortisei</a> and close to shops and restaurants. If one day you find yourself all ski-ed out then take some time to relax in the nearby Mardolimiti spa; the indoor pool, whirlpool and steam baths are free to use!</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Dolomiti Madonna the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
